message.entry: Input argument must be a cell array of character vectors.
Only one input argument is supported for cell arrays.
SORT on complex integers is not supported.
''ComparisonMethod'' parameter not supported when first argument is a {0} array.
''MissingPlacement'' parameter not supported when first argument is a {0} array.
Incorrect number of arguments. Parameter names and values must occur in pairs.
Dimension argument must be a positive integer.
Second argument must specify a dimension or a sorting direction.
Sorting direction must be a character vector.
